---
title: Grilled Cali-Style Beef and Pork Burgers with Green Goddess Sauce and Grilled Sweet Potatoes
description: It's summertime and we're bringing you sunny California goodness in a burger! Did someone say green goddess sauce? Juicy beef and pork patties topped with this addictive sauce will mean plates are clear in no time (and everyone loves a side of grilled sweet potatoes!). This dish is vibrant, fun and easy for weeknight grilling.
